high_descs: Turn to stand in front of the stove.
Open the cabinet on the left, above the stove and take out the green cup.
Turn to face the sink.
Put the cup in the sink, turn on the water and then turn it off and pick the cup up from the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave and shut the door and turn it on.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup in the microwave to warm it.

high_descs: Turn right and look above the stove
Open the cupboard directly above the stove and remove the green cup
Turn right and walk to the kitchen sink
Rinse the cup under water in the sink then remove it
Turn left and face the microwave on the counter
Put the cup into the microwave and close it
anns.task_desc: Put the washed green cup in the microwave

high_descs: Go to the stove on your right and face it.
Get the green tumbler from the cabinet slightly to the left above the stove.
Turn right and take the tumbler to the sink.
Wash the tumbler at the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Put the tumbler in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean green tumbler into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and face to your left
Open a kitchen cabinet and grab a green cup out of it
Turn right, to face the sink
Rinse the cup in the sink and pick the cup up out of the sink
Turn to face your left
Open the microwave, place the cup in it and turn it on
anns.task_desc: Rinse a cup and microwave it

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove on your left.
Open the cabinet above the left side of the stove, pick up the green glass and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the silver sink.
Put the glass inside the sink, rinse it off and pick it back up.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Place the glass inside the microwave on the blue plate and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean glass in a microwave.
